下来，我们发现电话居然都停了机――大家仿佛都忘记了我们的手机卡并不是本地卡――但是却一无所获。大家都有点心灰意冷，这是我们这辈子被别人拒绝最多的一天，而且这天的被拒绝比我们有生以来所有的被拒绝加一起还要多――打了多少电话，就有多少拒绝！<span><\/span><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\"><span>　　下班之前，“领导”继续给我们鼓励，说这没什么，毕竟是第一次，这比他以前强多了，而且还夸我们能成长的这么快确实不简单。<span><\/span><\/span><\/p><\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"11-10-03 13:55","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2011-10-03 13:55:26","ShortDate":"10-03 13:55","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d151641155.u21520390.htm","UserID":21520390,"UserName":"孤自幽伤曲","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":150,"v_lPageCount":6.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_152_0\">从今天起到国庆结束，每天保持两次更新。<\/div>\r\n","isAdminFlag":false,"isCanUpdate":false,"isDel":0,"isHide":0,"isShow":true,"keyThis":"","lDocModifiedCount":1,"LongDate":"11-10-03 14:00","online":false,"really_updated_at":"2011-10-03 14:00:16","ShortDate":"10-03 14:00","ShortDate_i":[],"Url":"/d151641155.u21520390.htm","UserID":21520390,"UserName":"孤自幽伤曲","UseVote":false,"v_isAdminDeleted":false,"v_isAppend":false,"v_isEditOwnDoc":false,"v_lDocModifiedPageNo":0,"v_lDocNo":151,"v_lPageCount":6.00000000000000000e+000,"v_lUserID":0,"v_lUserLevel":100,"v_SeeUserId":0},"isfirstfloor":false},{"docinfo":{},"foolrinfo":{"del_w":false,"DelTime":"","Emote":0,"fd_1_sel_product":false,"fd_id":0,"floorcontent":"<div class=doc_txt  id=\"text_153_0\">今天起早了，谢谢楼主给我们分享人生经历。<div align=\"right\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\r\n<tr><td class=\"doc_sign\" align=\"center\">\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td class=\"doc_sign\">&nbsp;　&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/table>\r\n<\/td><\/tr>\r\n